Dear Mike,

A good recent account is in:

A. Carboni, G. Janelidze, G. M. Kelly, and R. Par\'e, On localization
and stabilization for factorization systems, Applied Categorical
Structures (1997), no. 1, 1=E2=80=9358.

Richard

